### Register author
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"author2",
    "lastName":"",
    "email":"author2@gmail.com",
    "password":"author2",
    "role":"AUTHOR",
    "profileImageUrl":""
}

### Create new Article
POST http://localhost:5000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author":"69b3a7cedf3d69c983bbd430",
    "title":"Article 2 by author1",
    "category":"Technology",
    "content":"test article on ai"
}

### Update Article
PUT http://localhost:5000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleId":"69b3bed9f2227eae7e6626ed",
    "title":"Article 1 by author1",
    "category":"programming",
    "content":"test article on java and updated"
}

###make author login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"author1@gmail.com",
    "password":"author1"
}

### Author logout
GET http://localhost:5000/auth/logout

### Read own articles
GET http://localhost:5000/author-api/article

###Delete article by articleId(soft delete)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleId":"",
    "isArticleActivate":false
}